review: Dr. JayKishore is phenomenal in his line of work. We were consulting with him since the first day our daughter was born. He is extremely gentle, polite and very friendly. He remains calm even while dealing with critical situations. I’d recommend him.

*** *** ******* ** *** **** ****** *** **** ****** He is very polite and always listen to your problems , you can contact him at any point time and you will find him available for the required support and help.  He is like a god for me and my family,  he has treated my son in the best possible way and extended his support and cooperation always.
** *** ******* *** ** **** ****** *** ********* **** ** ** **** *** ** ** * Very polite and always listens to the parents of child. Thank You so much sir
